{"tid":1970767,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［多圖］政府搵警員扮鬼","createTime":"2020-04-13T11:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T11:54:55.000Z","uid":139194,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"07d738958163f9b8754264ea13824962320b63cf","tid":1970767,"uid":139194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:47:17.000Z","msg":"為防止民眾外出 印尼小鎮義工警員齊扮鬼嚇人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SMWxpE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SMWxpE.jpg&h=39e354ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情在印尼持續，當局亦加強防疫措施。印尼中部爪哇省（Java）小鎮坎古（Canggu），其中一個社區Sukoharjo為了呼應政府防疫政策，義工團體與警員想出在晚上扮鬼嚇人的方法，望藉此讓一些民眾可乖乖居於家中。<br />\n<br />\n提議該方法的義工團體表示，他們與警方一起合作執行，從四月初起，兩名義工包裹在白布裡，裝扮成當地著名傳說鬼怪婆娑鬼，在社區裡學殭屍跳動，希望民眾因此乖乖留在家裡。<br />\n<br />\n但沒想到，這些假鬼卻成了網紅現象，反吸引更多民眾在晚間跑出門，就只為看一眼。為此，推行單位只好不再固定派出殭屍巡邏，而是改為游擊戰措施，每周隨機選幾日出動鬼。<br />\n<br />\n義工組織指，扮鬼嚇人的措施雖然可見成效，但仍有不少青少年無視勸喻，聚集在街道上玩樂，又指當地民眾還是缺乏防疫意識，只想要過正常生活，因此不願遵守政府指示。<strong></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輕鬆下啦，香港人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1745919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1745919&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWUigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=99fa82de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1745919</a>"},{"pid":"7a42321b3d6e683f2848ad7c9c5dbf1dde54dc6a","tid":1970767,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"仲以為香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdad6755b38b2c74ca2e5bf946b5f01e384597df","tid":1970767,"uid":43178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"想喺香港試下做義工<br />\n不過要同黑警合作都係不了"},{"pid":"c87190ee19f9006401d314de6a8bda13d2c9455d","tid":1970767,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:54:55.000Z","msg":"香港都有警員上連登搞鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n示威現場又有便衣狗內鬼"}]}